Titolo: Mr. Cool (video game)

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: Mr. Cool is an action game designed by Peter Oliphant and published in 1983 by Sierra On-Line for the Atari 8-bit and Commodore 64. The ports for the Apple II and IBM PC (as a self-booting disk) were written by John Redekopp and released the same year. The game is heavily inspired by 1982 arcade Q*bert.